<subSubSection id="C3116523FF90A530CFEBC4AAFADDA31F" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB436A8FF90A530CFEBC4AAFADDA31F" blockId="41.[151,1436,874,1340]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">
<emphasis id="B97FEABAFF90A530CFEBC4AAFEA0A337" bold="true" box="[198,313,1274,1300]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Remarks.</emphasis>
Except 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9A4B59FF90A530CEB3C4AAFDA3A337" author="Kohn, A. J." box="[414,570,1274,1300]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" pagination="357 - 362" refId="ref43801" refString="Kohn, A. J. (2001) The Conidae of India revisited. Phuket Marine Biological Centre Special Publication, 25, 357 - 362." type="journal article" year="2001">Kohn (2001)</bibRefCitation>
, no previous record of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0B4D2BFF90A530CC79C4ABFC42A337" box="[852,987,1275,1300]" class="Gastropoda" family="Conidae" genus="Conus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="pertusus">
<emphasis id="B97FEABAFF90A530CC79C4ABFC42A337" box="[852,987,1275,1300]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">C. pertusus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from 
<collectingCountry id="F31C7638FF90A530CBB2C4AAFB46A337" box="[1183,1247,1274,1300]" name="India" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">India</collectingCountry>
. This species is probably restricted to the Gulf of Mannar and appears to be a rare species along the 
<collectingRegion id="49CFF84AFF90A530CB42C572FB6BA31F" box="[1135,1266,1314,1340]" country="India" name="Tamil Nadu" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">TamilNadu</collectingRegion>
Coast.
</paragraph>
